{"tid":1918140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(3月10日) 西藏發生武裝衝突  達賴逃亡","createTime":"2020-03-10T01:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T04:14:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ee27630a198d0c4b16958a883edcd1b3f0baa5","tid":1918140,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:57:53.000Z","msg":"1959年3月10日，西藏人因不滿中國政府高壓統治，與解放軍在拉薩發生武裝衝突，也開啟了達賴喇嘛的流亡生涯。<br />\n<br />\n1959年3月10日，西藏人民與解放軍在拉薩發生武裝衝突，抗議從1950年中國軍隊進入後，採取的高壓統治。7天後，藏人不敵解放軍的鎮壓，原本領導西藏政府的第十四世達賴喇嘛，開始了流亡生涯。此後3月10日被訂為西藏的人民起義日，每年舉辦紀念活動或是示威抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/general/202003/202003101993146.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fcts%2Fgeneral%2F202003%2F202003101993146.html&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=5749d318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/general/202003/202003101993146.html</a>"},{"pid":"002137b6d1ec79a24156f250338985fd735a0635","tid":1918140,"uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.ipkmedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/%E9%99%B3%E5%B7%A7%E6%96%87-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A-20200113204414_1249_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipkmedia.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25B7%25A7%25E6%2596%2587-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A-20200113204414_1249_large.png&h=0bae2bcf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b80603413f2ba9b1ee431be51e0f0110201cf8f0","tid":1918140,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T04:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.ipkmedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/%E9%99%B3%E5%B7%A7%E6%96%87-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A-20200113204414_1249_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipkmedia.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25B7%25A7%25E6%2596%2587-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E